|GKB-- Sky Blade -------------------------------------------------|000

Current: |CKBTekali|000
Command: |CKBskyblade <type>|000
Guild Level: 9

Sky Blade shapes a temporary scythe-like weapon from the sky.  Its
weapon class and duration follow the same scale as a cleric's spiritual
hammer.  The default type is magic.  Other types become available
through alignment and mastery.

Mastery expands the available damage forms.

At Druid guild level 10, |CKBTwin Sky Blades|000 lets you shape two Sky
Blades at once:

  |CKBtwinskyblades <type>|000

It costs the same Tekali nwyfre as casting Sky Blade twice, but avoids
waiting through the cooldown between the two invocations.
